snippet.title: The Remake of the End of the Greatest RPG of All Time - Official Trailer
snippet.description: The Remake of the End of the Greatest RPG of All Time is the last hour of a lost (nonexistent) JRPG, "remade” in 3D pixel art complete with director’s commentary, the digital manual, and archival footage. Using these material players deduce how to complete the "ending" of this game without the context of the first 99 percent, turning this RPG into a puzzle game. Check out The Remake of the End of the Greatest RPG of All Time to see what to expect. A Kickstarter campaign for The Remake of the End of the Greatest RPG of All Time is live now.
